data.description: Welcome Home to the beautiful Autumn Canyon Subdivision in Cartersville, GA! This well maintained community is nestled not too far from Lake Allatoona, Red Top Mountain State Park, the interstate, as well as, multiple shops & dining for your entertainment! As you walk into this gorgeous 4 bed, 2.5 bath home you will be greeted by the entrance foyer and immaculate hardwood floors throughout! The beautiful layout of this home has so much to offer with a large open concept living room and kitchen making it the perfect setting to entertain guests while preparing meals! In the kitchen you will find an island with granite countertops, walk-in pantry, stainless steel appliances, and dark cherry wood cabinets. Leading up the wide steps to the second floor you will find the oversized main bedroom, inside the main bathroom you will find a nicely decorative tiled standalone shower, as well as, a nicely decorative tiled soak-in tub with a large vanity, and oversized walk-in closet and standalone toilet. Each of the three guest bedrooms have a large window for some natural light, and nice sized closets. All of the windows have shutter plantation blinds. The fenced in backyard offers a covered patio with a ceiling fan for hot summers! The landscaping in the front and back yard have been maintained on this home. The front porch is long enough to put a bench out for enjoying your morning coffee, or tea. This home is not too far from the playground and gazebo in the neighborhood. Home is vacant so please schedule all showings through ShowingTime and wait for confirmation. Buyer's agent to verify all pertinent facts! Sellers looking for a quick close so send all offers! This home is less than 10 years old and all major components as well. This home is in great condition and has been well-kept. No Blind offers!!
